        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-e97cec74-a7fb-4993-96f5-a8f276b98353">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e97cec74-a7fb-4993-96f5-a8f276b98353">
                Lady Apsley
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e97cec74-a7fb-4993-96f5-a8f276b98353" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1943-07-21/debates/ff2186e2-4c77-45ef-8c33-af48e550dc8f/VictoriaCross(Pensions)#contribution-e97cec74-a7fb-4993-96f5-a8f276b98353">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister whether, as a result of further consideration, he will increase the present annual grant of £10 to a holder of the Victoria Cross?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e97cec74-a7fb-4993-96f5-a8f276b98353" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1943-07-21/debates/ff2186e2-4c77-45ef-8c33-af48e550dc8f/VictoriaCross(Pensions)#contribution-e97cec74-a7fb-4993-96f5-a8f276b98353">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-2ec5f03d-02e2-40cd-a731-8c947a487e66">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-2ec5f03d-02e2-40cd-a731-8c947a487e66">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-2ec5f03d-02e2-40cd-a731-8c947a487e66">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-2ec5f03d-02e2-40cd-a731-8c947a487e66">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2ec5f03d-02e2-40cd-a731-8c947a487e66" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1943-07-21/debates/ff2186e2-4c77-45ef-8c33-af48e550dc8f/VictoriaCross(Pensions)#contribution-2ec5f03d-02e2-40cd-a731-8c947a487e66">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As my right hon. Friend the Deputy Prime Minister informed my hon. Friend on 29th June, the normal pensions payable to recipients of the Victoria Cross may be increased in cases of need to £75. This <span id="890" class="column-number" data-column-number="890"></span> figure was fixed in 1921. Further inquiries have been made, but they do not show any evidence of general complaint as to the adequacy of this special provision. I do not think any change in this well-established practice is called for.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2ec5f03d-02e2-40cd-a731-8c947a487e66" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1943-07-21/debates/ff2186e2-4c77-45ef-8c33-af48e550dc8f/VictoriaCross(Pensions)#contribution-2ec5f03d-02e2-40cd-a731-8c947a487e66">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-10cd2e8e-aa52-42ff-9917-a0613a7e081c">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-10cd2e8e-aa52-42ff-9917-a0613a7e081c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-10cd2e8e-aa52-42ff-9917-a0613a7e081c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-10cd2e8e-aa52-42ff-9917-a0613a7e081c">
                Lady Apsley
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-10cd2e8e-aa52-42ff-9917-a0613a7e081c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1943-07-21/debates/ff2186e2-4c77-45ef-8c33-af48e550dc8f/VictoriaCross(Pensions)#contribution-10cd2e8e-aa52-42ff-9917-a0613a7e081c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is my right hon. Friend aware that there has been no material change in this rate since 1857 for the ordinary recipients of the Victoria Cross? Does he not agree, in view of present-day values, that £10 is nothing more than an insult to a fighting man and that in order to be equal to its original value that sum ought to be £50 or even £100?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-10cd2e8e-aa52-42ff-9917-a0613a7e081c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1943-07-21/debates/ff2186e2-4c77-45ef-8c33-af48e550dc8f/VictoriaCross(Pensions)#contribution-10cd2e8e-aa52-42ff-9917-a0613a7e081c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-a513761f-0f9a-4671-afd4-8954c8e4a13c">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-a513761f-0f9a-4671-afd4-8954c8e4a13c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-a513761f-0f9a-4671-afd4-8954c8e4a13c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a513761f-0f9a-4671-afd4-8954c8e4a13c">
                The Primo Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a513761f-0f9a-4671-afd4-8954c8e4a13c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1943-07-21/debates/ff2186e2-4c77-45ef-8c33-af48e550dc8f/VictoriaCross(Pensions)#contribution-a513761f-0f9a-4671-afd4-8954c8e4a13c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I do not think this is a matter to be settled entirely on a money basis, and I do not propose to advise the House to make any change.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a513761f-0f9a-4671-afd4-8954c8e4a13c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1943-07-21/debates/ff2186e2-4c77-45ef-8c33-af48e550dc8f/VictoriaCross(Pensions)#contribution-a513761f-0f9a-4671-afd4-8954c8e4a13c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-3a585cba-6c53-4a25-a78f-f80acaffce77">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-3a585cba-6c53-4a25-a78f-f80acaffce77">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-3a585cba-6c53-4a25-a78f-f80acaffce77">
