<p class="">Does the Prime Minister realise that the award of the D.C.M. carries with it 6d. a day and that the award which goes with the Victoria Cross would work out at just under 7d. per day in value?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
